ActFederal Public Sector Labour Relations Act
SubjectCFIA-PIPSC- Professional Institute of the Public Service of Canada **Collective Agreement** Informatics (IN) Bargaining Unit.
PrecisOrder authorizing the CANADIAN FOOD INSPECTION AGENCY to enter into a COLLECTIVE AGREEMENT with the PROFESSIONAL INSTITUTE OF THE PUBLIC SERVICE OF CANADA (PIPSC) applicable to all employees of the Agency for the Informatics (IN) Bargaining Unit, which provides for the changes to the previous Collective Agreement which expires on May 31, 2018.
